race.description: Lvtc 2025 Melbourne Cup Calcutta 2nd Nov Hcp
race.comment: DAZZLING DIAMOND (5) is a consistent conveyance who has only missed the top-four once in eight career starts and doesn't know how to put in a poor one. Gets in well at the weights with the 3kg claim and should be right there at the business end. GOLD FEVER (1) resumes here but the form he showed when last in work was good enough for a race of this calibre. Can run a big race while fresh. WISE CHOICE (8) has placed around this circuit and gets the reliable Webster/Tilley combination. One of the better hopes. SPIRIT OF NURAI (7) is another resuming but has placed two of four when first-up. Respect any market confidence. BOMBISCUIT (10) next in line.
